{"tid":2099481,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"美國政府開口牌：投資支國公司，未來或會因支國受制裁而令投資虧損","createTime":"2020-07-08T09:07:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-08T11:51:00.000Z","uid":48040,"like":78,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"c622161acde074e7ab350bec410824ba0dd79cdb","tid":2099481,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T09:07:39.000Z","msg":"白宮官員警告由聯邦管理的鐵路工人退休基金，不應該向中國公司投資，因為可能會出台更多的制裁措施，投資者可能因此蒙受損失。<br />\n<br />\n國家安全顧問羅伯特&middot;C&middot;奧布賴恩(Robert C. O'Brien)和國家經濟委員會主任拉里&middot;庫德洛(Larry Kudlow)在給聯邦鐵路職工退休基金(US Railroad Retirement Board)的一封信中說，<span style=\"color: orange;\">其在中國的投資使退休人員面臨&ldquo;不必要的經濟風險&rdquo;。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://cn.nytimes.com/business/20200708/white-house-chinese-investment/?utm_source=tw-nytimeschinese&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_campaign=cur\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcn.nytimes.com%2Fbusiness%2F20200708%2Fwhite-house-chinese-investment%2F%3Futm_source%3Dtw-nytimeschinese%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_campaign%3Dcur&d=68p4wiGQQ1h%2Fwz3iobjDK%2F3Ut%2FTlF5atQuTXJDR4vuI%3D&h=65a8901b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://cn.nytimes.com/business/20200708/white-house-chinese-investment/?utm_source=tw-nytimeschinese&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_campaign=cur</a><br />\n<br />\n簡單一句：即係白宮叫國內退休基金唔好投資中國公司，因為將來一旦制裁，投資就會虧損。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SomethinkMore/status/1280788966032076801?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSomethinkMore%2Fstatus%2F1280788966032076801%3Fs%3D20&d=68p4wiGQQ1h%2Fwz3iobjDK%2F3Ut%2FTlF5atQuTXJDR4vuI%3D&h=b47fb57b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSomethinkMore%2Fstatus%2F1280788966032076801%3Fs%3D20&h=cab227f1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SomethinkMore/status/1280788966032076801?s=20</a>"},{"pid":"ad496f6d0f8d2d950d37b8b590cae71ee2ab9c42","tid":2099481,"uid":144626,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0